messages.content: Thanks, Tally. It's not as impressive as your autorifle, but it gets the job done. How's your ammo holding up? Do you need me to resupply you?
messages.speaker: Kyle Newton

messages.content: Hey there E.Kristensen, how are you doing today? Ready for our next mission?
messages.speaker: [DoD]Matrix

messages.content: Great to hear it! I've been going over our supply inventory and everything looks good to go. We should have all the ammo and equipment we need for this mission. Have you checked your gear and weapon to make sure everything's in working order?
messages.speaker: [DoD]Matrix

messages.content: Excellent, glad to hear it. We can't afford any malfunctions out there! Is there anything else you need from the supply room before we head out?
messages.speaker: [DoD]Matrix
